OL,3,CFire service governance 'needs to
OL,4,Cchange', committee chair says
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government needs to come up
OL,7,Fwith an alternative way to run fire
OL,8,Fservices in Wales, a Sharp End panel
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FJenny Rathbone MS, who chairs the
OL,12,Fcommittee tasked with scrutinising the
OL,13,Fculture of fire and rescue services,
OL,14,Fsaid the governance "needs to change".
OL,16,FHer comments come ahead of two
OL,17,Ftroubled Welsh fire services
OL,18,Fpublishing the findings of a review
OL,19,Finto their culture later today.
