OL,4,Cchange', committee chair says
OL,6,FAn investigation by ITV Wales saw more
OL,7,Fthan 35 whistleblowers raising serious
OL,8,Fconcerns about behaviour in the North
OL,9,FWales and Mid and West Wales Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Services.
OL,12,FThe Senedd's Equality and Social
OL,13,FJustice Committee previously
OL,14,Frecommended that the Welsh government
OL,15,Fmake clear that fire service staff
OL,16,Fcoming forward with complaints will be
OL,17,Fadequately supported and treated
OL,18,Ffairly, alongside urgently exploring
OL,19,Foptions for "more radical reform" in
OL,20,Fthe long term.
