OL,3,CFire service governance 'needs to
OL,4,Cchange', committee chair says
OL,6,FShe said: "The people who were on the
OL,7,Ffire authorities simply weren't asking
OL,8,Fenough of the right questions and were
OL,9,Fbeing dismissed as unable to be
OL,10,Fproperly managing the governance of
OL,11,Fthe organisation because it was all
OL,12,Ftoo technical."
OL,14,FThe committee found that the roles
OL,15,Fwere given as "consolation prizes" to
OL,16,Fcouncillors who didn't get chairs of
OL,17,Fcommittees.
