OL,3,CFire service governance 'needs to
OL,4,Cchange', committee chair says
OL,6,FWorkplace culture at the Welsh fire
OL,7,Fservices has been under the spotlight
OL,8,Ffor some time.
OL,10,FITV Wales revealed allegations of a
OL,11,Ftoxic culture at both North Wales Fire
OL,12,Fand Rescue Service and Mid and West
OL,13,FWales Fire and Rescue Service earlier
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, a damning culture review at
OL,17,FSouth Wales' service was published in
OL,18,FJanuary 2024 and was sparked by an ITV
OL,19,FNews investigation into claims of
OL,20,Fabuse and harassment of female staff
OL,21,Fby male firefighters.
